                                            <i class="ri-star-fill"></i>
                                            <i class="ri-star-fill"></i>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic">"Outstanding quality and attention to detail.
                                        The perfect blend of style and functionality. Will definitely order again!"</p>
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div
                                            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600 font-bold mr-4">
                                            <i class="ri-user-line"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <h4 class="font-semibold" style="color: #1E1E1E;">Michael Chen</h4>
                                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Verified Customer</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4">
                                <div class="p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg"
